room_title: Escape room "Escape From Marie's Children" by Immersion in Marysville
room_description:
You are part of the Dark Division: an elite underground agency hired by the Illuminati to find a cursed medallion. The Dark Division’s reputation is one that is known among the most elite. You have been paid a hefty sum in advance and provided Marie’s last known location of the medallion Marysville WA. As part of the Dark Division, failure is not an option!
Marie Bishop, a famous dollmaker, born in the early 1800s, was the last known person to have it and rumors say she still has it. You and your team will only have 60 minutes to retrieve the medallion. Find clues to solve the mystery surrounding the medallion and why the Illuminati have hired you to find it for them.
